<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77ebff38-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s77ll"><num value="77ll">§ 77ll.</num><heading> Effective date of subchapter</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">This subchapter shall not take effect until the President finds that its taking effect is in the public interest and by proclamation so declares.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77ebff39-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">(<ref href="/us/act/1933-05-27/ch38">May 27, 1933, ch. 38</ref>, title II, § 211, <ref href="/us/stat/48/95">48 Stat. 95</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
